{"title":"cocom_help","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"markdown":"* This panel focuses on the **Code Complexity** metrics and their evolution
* **Selector** :
  * **Repository** helps results for a given repository
  * **Module Path** helps refine results for a given module
  * **interval_months** is the study interval (default: 1)
* **Repositories** gives an overview of all the repositories and the corresponding metrics
* **Overall Complexity & Functions** gives the latest overall sum of Code Complexity and Functions of the repositories
* **Evolution: Code Complexity and Functions** shows the evolution of the Code Complexity and Functions over the time period
* **Overall LOC & Comments** gives the latest overall sum of Lines of Code and Comment of the repositories
* **Evolution: LOC & Comments** shows the evolution of the Lines of Code and Comments over the time period
* **All Files: Code complexity, LOC and ratios** gives metrics corresponding to each file of the repository, which can be delegated via the Module Path Selector



[See complete panel documentation]()"},"aggs":[]}
